Package: ggplot2PlanetPalettes
Type: Package
Title: Color Palettes Inspired by Celestial Bodies for ggplot2
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Luca", "Tonietti", email = "astrobio.it@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
)
Description: Provides color palettes for ggplot2 inspired by the appearance and characteristics of celestial bodies in the Solar System. The package includes discrete and continuous palettes for planets, moons, and asteroids.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: ggplot2
